headline: SUPER BOWL LIX ON FOX AND TUBI GENERATES MORE THAN $800 MILLION IN GROSS ADVERTISING REVENUE
summary: Fox Corporation (NASDAQ: FOXA) (NASDAQ: FOX) today announced that the presentation of Super Bowl LIX on FOX and Tubi generated over $800 Million in gross revenue from advertising sales across all platforms, with record pricing for the sold-out game.
